Nada Brahma

Vibrational Arts

Nada Brahma exists to hold space for group and individual growth by revealing the healer residing in each of us.

Sessions are offered for groups or individuals, and may include sacred sound, breathwork, and divine energy channeling to awaken our innate ability to heal ourselves physically, emotionally, and spiritually.

Each session is unique and tailored to the individual or group need.
